Abarwayi banduye HCoV-229E bagaragaje ibimenyetso by’ibicurane bisanzwe, twavuga nk’umutwe, kwitsamura, kumererwa nabi no kubabara mu muhogo, hamwe n’umuriro n’inkorora byabonetse mu 10~20% by’abarwayi.
Nyuma y’aho muri 1967, HCoV-OC43 yabonetse mu rugingo rw’umubiri iza no kugaragara mu bwonko bw’imbeba zonsa.
ጸኒሑ ኣብ 1967 HCoV-OC43  ካብ ህዋስ ምርባሕን ዝስዕብ ተኻታታሊ መተሓላለፊ ኣብ ኣእምሮ ናይ ውልዶ ኣናጹ ተፈልዩ ኔሩ።
Ibimenyetso byo kwa muganga by’indwara ya HCoV-OC43 usanga bisa n’ibiterwa na HCoV-229E, bikaba bidashobora gutandukanywa n’indwara iterwa n’izindi virusi zibasira imyanya y’ubuhumekero nka virusi zitera ibicurane by’ibiguruka na virusi zitera ibicurane bisanzwe.
ናይ HCoV-OC43 ክሊኒካዊ ምልክታት፡ ምስቲ HCoV-229E ዝተሓሓዝ ኮይኑ፡ ካብ ካልኦት ናይ ምስትንፋስ ቫይረስታት ከም ናይ ወፍሪ ኢንፍሉዌንስ ቫይረስን ናይ ተራ ኢንፍሉዌንስ ቫይረስን ዝፍጠር ሕማም ኣይፍለን።
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 zombi ziboneka ku isi hose, kandi zikunda gukwirakwira cyane mu rugaryi hari ibihe bihehereye.
